snippet: Notre Dame running back Cierre Wood will not be back for his final year of eligibility and will enter the N.F.L. draft.
abstract: Notre Dame running back Cierre Wood will enter the 2013 NFL draft rather than returning for his final year of eligibility; other college football news noted.

headline.main: Notre Dame Running Back Going Pro
